GOV.UK Pay Merge (#52)

* WIP Integration

* integration and api wip

* WIP integration with govuk pay

* add methods for payment checks

* Added new model for payment_db

* Re-generated migration files

* Removed old payment models and tests

* update tests

* merge develop and add tests

* integrate with db and add tests WIP

* unit tests

* Update Dockerfile

* fix urls

* Added invoice_number column

* Added check for DB insert around invoice_number

* Included new endpoint for searching using invoice_number

* fix unit tests

* Update check for settlement summary

* allow URNs up to 9 chars

* fix migrations

* Created inital query and endpoint

* Created query function and application processing

* update check for payment already made

* Altered response to include application type

* Removed comment

* Removed migration

* Altered return contents for no applications

* prevent duplicate payment on pay

* Casted string env var to int

Co-authored-by: jenniferbrown94 <jennifer.brown@informed.com>
